text_raw:
2. The 18th day of November 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
Electricity Costs (Emergency Measures) Domestic Accounts Act 2023 (No. 29 
of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

17 November, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for Environment, Climate and Communications. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 21st November, 2023.
